Package gov.lbl.glamm.server.retrosynthesis

Class Summary
Route Class for conveniently representing routes between source and destination compounds.
Route.RouteComparator Compares two routes by total cost.
Route.Step Route step assigning a cost to a node in the metabolic network (where a node includes both source and destination compound, as well as the reaction used to link the two.)
